OL,3,CTrump sends "a lot of luck" as Gabriel
OL,4,CRaimondo is elected in St Brelade
OL,6,FNews of Gabriel Raimondo's election in
OL,7,FJersey reached the White House as
OL,8,FPresident of the United States Donald
OL,9,FTrump told ITV News to "wish him a lot
OL,10,Fof luck".
OL,12,FGabriel Raimondo is thought to be the
OL,13,Fworld's youngest parliamentarian after
OL,14,Fbeing elected as a Deputy of St
OL,15,FBrelade and has attracted global
OL,16,Fattention.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
