CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781100697
OL,3,CTrump sends "a lot of luck" as Gabriel
OL,4,CRaimondo is elected in St Brelade
OL,6,FWhen ITV asked President Trump about
OL,7,Fthe achievement in a phone call, he
OL,8,Fsaid that young people in politics are
OL,9,F"great" and "they have great
OL,10,Fimagination". He went on to "wish him
OL,11,Fa lot of luck".
OL,13,FWhen he was told about the President's
OL,14,Fcomments, Deputy-Elect Raimondo said
OL,15,Fthat it was "crazy" and that he agrees
OL,16,Fthat "youth in politics is brilliant."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
