OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781100697
OL,3,CTrump sends "a lot of luck" as Gabriel
OL,4,CRaimondo is elected in St Brelade
OL,6,FThe teenager delayed his A-Levels
OL,7,Funtil November to focus on his
OL,8,Felection campaign. He only turned 18,
OL,9,Fthe minimum qualifying age for
OL,10,Fcandidates, ten days before polling.
OL,12,FHis 1,603 votes saw him claim third
OL,13,Fplace in the St Brelade district
OL,14,Felection and a place in the island's
OL,15,Fassembly.
OL,17,FThe 18-year-old will now spend four
OL,18,Fyears in office and make decisions
OL,19,Fthat affect the roughly 100,000 people
OL,20,Fwho live in the self-governing Crown
OL,21,FDependency.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
