OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781100697
OL,3,CTrump sends "a lot of luck" as Gabriel
OL,4,CRaimondo is elected in St Brelade
OL,6,FUnlike Westminster, Jersey's
OL,7,FParliament is mainly made up of
OL,8,Findependents. Gabriel aligns himself
OL,9,Fwith the new political movement Value
OL,10,FJersey, which says it aims to make the
OL,11,Fisland more affordable.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/4
